AWS Lambda:
Memory: 128MB - 3008MB - CPU proportional
Ephemeral disk space: 512MB at /tmp
Max execution duration: 300 seconds or 5 minutes
Compressed package size: 50MB including node_modules/
Uncompressed package size: 250MB


